title: do not cum if you arachnaphobia
text:
Browse Channels Arachnophobics, you better look away 
Video of the nasty surprise shows the mammoth mother spider keeping a close watch over her hatchlings as they clamber out of their nest. The bite of a huntsman isn't dangerous to humans – it’s their fearsome appearance, and knack for crawling out of car dashboards, that’s the real concern. Courtesy: Noel Parminter, Auswise Pest control
